dialog{
  id = "moblin_inn.innkeeper",
  text = [[
Welcome to the Moblin's Head Inn, Princess!
Please sit a while.
Some very interesting folks pass through here,
so maybe you should talk to them.
You might learn something useful.
]]
}

dialog{
  id = "moblin_inn.lady",
  text = [[
Hello there! Why don't you sit a moment.
They say that deep in the earth one can overcome
the sins of greed. I don't really know what that
means, but I do know that greedy trolls like to
make their lairs in dark caves far to the south.
If you're going to go anywhere dark, you'll do
well to get yourself a lantern.
]]
}

dialog{
  id = "moblin_inn.patron",
  text = [[
You seem like the patient type. That's a
good trait to have. Don't surrender to the
things that seem impossible.
]]
}

dialog{
  id = "moblin_inn.traveler",
  text = [[
Oh man, I really should have made sure to bring
a lantern. You can't see anything stumbling
around in the dark! There was a stall in the
southern forest selling them, but I didn't think
I needed one so passed it by.
]]
}

